items.title: Awesome Iam
items.content_text:
### Authorization / AWS policy tools

*   [IAM Floyd (‚≠ê562)](https://github.com/udondan/iam-floyd) - AWS IAM policy statement generator with fluent interface. Helps with creating type safe IAM policies and writing more restrictive/secure statements by offering conditions and ARN generation via IntelliSense. Available for Node.js, Python, .Net and Java.
